summary.raw: Reduce likelihood of race condition by setting winchIndex to -1 in HarnessPlugin::OnDetach then actually calling HarnessPlugin::Detach in the Update loop, so that it will happen in the right thread. Also, update some assumptions in the test, since it now requires a world step before detaching the joint
